## Worktrees

When working as a role agent:

- Prefer using a dedicated git worktree for isolation.
- Use branch naming from `.orchestration/config/framework.yaml`:
  `cursor/<role>/<iteration-or-work-item>` for generated agent worktrees in
  this repository.
- Post a memo when ready-to-consume with branch + SHA.

